run1.title: Nate talks
run1.description: I talked with Nate about runs back at home, LoZ, any random stuff. My legs felt good, they are still recovering from the workout and the races last weekend, but they felt better then I was expecting them to. My sleep wasn't the best last night, I should do better at that, but overall I felt good today. Really starting to gear up for the end of the season.
